{"tid":12522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新空管系統有26秒未能顯示航班資料 當局認不符理想","createTime":"2016-11-29T16:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T17:03:18.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df6528b737bcf15e091e998eeff994b7e0bff904","tid":12522,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"民航處處長李天柱表示，新的空管系統今日下午有大約26秒時間未能顯示航班的部分資料，空管人員為保障安全，暫停處理離境航班15分鐘。<br />\n李天柱表示，據承辦商工程師初步分析，主要是航班數據處理器，自動將資料存檔時，遇到問題。<br />\n他承認表現不符理想，已要求承辦商高層來港跟進，並責成承辦商48小時內提交報告，及提出解決方案。"},{"pid":"e79d560aff8f05dcd27de9a27091cf97d0ed8aeb","tid":12522,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b679c32be28cf119435492b9c994c7eb62672a","tid":12522,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"其實新系統係邊度技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d81ffb600a0bcbd2d2cf90872a297d89cc4573e","tid":12522,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c42e9dd46a5286d5b9a3e1702ab1911a6eda279","tid":12522,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實新系統係邊度技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢搭。好戇鳩"},{"pid":"aa6fe764d648ee172e7c2ab068866b7bdc433230","tid":12522,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"成件事好醜惡<br />\n唔知係貪平定方便利益輸送係要買<br />\n都講左得三個機場用<br />\n好喇到真係用時<br />\n明明有問題出現就死撐<br />\n到撐唔住就賴供應商<br />\n究竟而家個政府有無正常小小既人"},{"pid":"1b61753622855523484495fd80c2818e962cfd38","tid":12522,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成件事好醜惡<br 